<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"/>
  <title>Vistazo</title>
  
  <link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Cabin:400,700,400italic' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/fonts/fonts.css" type="text/css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" type="text/css" />
  <% if @projects.present? %>
    <style type="text/css">
      <% for project in @projects %>
        <%= ".#{project.css_class}" %> {
          background-color: <%= "#{project.hex_colour}" %>;
        }
      <% end %>
    </style>
  <% end %>
  
  <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.6.4/jquery.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
  <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jqueryui/1.8.16/jquery-ui.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
  <script src="/js/jquery.labelify.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
  <script src="/js/underscore-min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
  <script src="/js/backbone-min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
  <script src="/js/script.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
</head>
<body class="homepage">
  <div id="top-nav">
    <h1>VISTAZO</h1>
    <a href="/auth/google_oauth2/">Sign in</a>
  </div>
  
  <%= styled_flash %>
  
  <div id="main">
    <img id="screenshot" src="img/pixel-vistazo.png" alt="" />
    <div id="intro">Team management from the fine folks at <a href="http://pebblecode.com/"><img src="img/pebble.png" alt="pebble {code}" /></a></div>
    <div id="outro">
      <p>Vistazo is free, easy to use, and mind-alteringly awesome. All you need is a Google acount.</p>
      <a id="start-btn" href="/auth/google_oauth2/">Start using vistazo</a>
      <h3><img src="img/down-arrow.png" alt="" />just a few reasons you'll love Vistazo<img src="img/down-arrow.png" alt="" /></h3>
    </div>
    <div id="glance">
      <img src="img/glance.png" alt="" />
      <div class="home-right">
        <h2>At a glance</h2>
        <p>Quickly see who on your team is working on what, when.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="abc">
      <img src="img/abc.png" alt="" />
      <div class="home-right">
        <h2>As easy as...</h2>
        <p><span>1.</span> Add people to your team. <span>2.</span> Add projects to team members. <span>3.</span> Profit. Yup thatâ€™s it. Super simple team management even your nan could understand.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="day">
      <img src="img/day.png" alt="" />
      <div class="home-right">
        <h2>Day by day</h2>
        <p>Vistazo works with days, not hours, not minutes. Cut out the micro management and let your team structure their own workdays.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="demo">
      <img src="img/demo.png" alt="" />
      <div class="home-right">
        <h2>Democratic</h2>
        <p>In Vistazo everyone is equal. All users can view & edit any element within a team.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <%= erb :_footer %>
  
</body>